      • getFieldData

        public java.util.List<?> getFieldData(@NonNull
                                      @NonNull java.lang.String fieldName,
                                      int indexOfTarget)
        Gets data for an output field which is specified by search request. Throws ParamException if the field doesn't exist. Throws ParamException if the indexOfTarget is illegal.
        参数:
        fieldName - field name to get output data
        indexOfTarget - which target vector the field data belongs to
        返回:
        FieldDataWrapper

      • getIDScore

        public java.util.List<SearchResultsWrapper.IDScore> getIDScore(int indexOfTarget)
                                                        throws ParamException,
                                                               IllegalResponseException
        Gets ID-score pairs returned by search interface. Throws ParamException if the indexOfTarget is illegal. Throws IllegalResponseException if the returned results is illegal.
        参数:
        indexOfTarget - which target vector the result belongs to
        返回:
        List<IDScore> ID-score pairs returned by search interface
        抛出:
        ParamException
        IllegalResponseException
